          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photoneutron angular  distributions  from  carbon",
                " and   beryllium   have   been   measured   by  using",
                " bremsstrahlung of maximum energies of 23 and 18 MeV,",
                " respectively.  The  angular  distributions  obtained",
                " are:  1 + (1.35 (0.88)) * (sin(theta))**2 for carbon",
                " and (1.26 (0.11)) + (sin(theta))**2 for beryllium."
              ]
            }
          ],
